## üîÆ Future Plans

We hope this project becomes the default way for people who are unfamiliar with Polkadot code to start a Polkadot project.

We intend to keep the LLM instructions and boilerplates up-to-date (or synced with the right documentation), so that it continues to build useful Dapps.

We will also seek grant and VC funding to expand the business to more project types, reducing the technical barrier to building Web3 projects!


